{"tid":1537484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英首相約翰遜對香港嚴峻局勢感憂慮  促維護言論及集會自由","createTime":"2019-09-04T02:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T03:12:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ef1d87365f8d53062783da67ee62a7b485bd40bb","tid":1537484,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190904/_2019090410395776110.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190904%2F_2019090410395776110.jpg&h=f2c444ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n( AP圖)<br />\n<br />\n英國下議院短暫復會，英國首相約翰遜在國會發言時表示，對香港目前嚴峻局勢感到憂慮，強調必須維護香港的言論及集會自由。他說，相信整個下議院亦與他的看法一樣，英國堅決維護香港在「一國兩制」下所保障的生活方式，他又對七國集團就香港議題的立場，給予堅定支持。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜又感謝七國集團峰會早前發表聲明時亦提及香港局勢。另外，外相藍韜文發言指，留意到香港部份示威演變成暴力，指警方對示威者使用武力的問題，有需要展開可以得到港人信任的獨立調查。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1583425/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%B4%84%E7%BF%B0%E9%81%9C%E5%B0%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9A%B4%E5%B3%BB%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2%E6%84%9F%E6%86%82%E6%85%AE-%E4%BF%83%E7%B6%AD%E8%AD%B7%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E5%8F%8A%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1</code></pre>"},{"pid":"dce62f053478c4beedc6e302fadf9a3dd0547438","tid":1537484,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:49:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"253f59505b60af5e38efb6304f2034d73899e965","tid":1537484,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:49:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n唔該入去幫p牌仔推一推 好人一世平安<br />\n<br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLDFcUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLDFcUN.jpg&h=350c6ca1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07ac8880a62cf01e267032f0354c87f5d2d55e7f","tid":1537484,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQ0Tyrc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQ0Tyrc.jpg&h=d900eccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a>"},{"pid":"23ad8631d1a7c903a7981de7d7db2b9779becc76","tid":1537484,"uid":14918,"li